Label the concentric “rings’’ of the hexagonal spiral by  
n = 0 (the centre 1), n = 1 (numbers 2 … 7), n = 2 (numbers 8 … 19) and in
general

 largest number of ring n : L(n)=1+3n(n+1)  
 first number of ring n   : F(n)=L(n-1)+1 = 2+3(n−1)n

Every ring n (n≥1) contains 6n numbers and consists of 6 sides, each
containing n numbers, except that on the last (east) side only the first
n–1 belong to the ring.  
Inside one side the numbers are consecutive; going from the (k–1)-st to
the k-th side we simply add n.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
1.  Which ring holds 2026?
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Solve 1+3n(n+1) ≥ 2026 :

 n = 25 ⇒ L(25)=1951 < 2026  
 n = 26 ⇒ L(26)=2107 ≥ 2026

So 2026 lies on ring n = 26.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
2.  Where on this ring is 2026?
--------------------------------------------------------------------
First number of the ring

 F(26)=2+3·25·26 = 1952

Offset of 2026 in the ring

 t = 2026 – 1952 = 74  (0-based)

Side length = n = 26.

Side index s = ⌊74/26⌋ = 2    (the 3rd side: the “western’’ side)  
Position on the side m = 74 mod 26 = 22 (counting 0,1,…,25)

--------------------------------------------------------------------
3.  The six neighbours
--------------------------------------------------------------------
• two on the same ring    2025   (=2026–1) and 2027 (=2026+1)

For the remaining four we only have to know how the shorter inner side
(n–1) and the longer outer side (n+1) line up with the present side.

Inner ring (n-1 = 25)

 F(25)=2+3·24·25 = 1802  
 offset on that ring = s·(n-1)+m  (= 2·25+22 = 72) and one less

 → 1802 + 71 = 1873  
 → 1802 + 72 = 1874

Outer ring (n+1 = 27)

 F(27)=2+3·26·27 = 2108  
 offset on that ring = s·(n+1)+m  (= 2·27+22 = 76) and one more

 → 2108 + 76 = 2184  
 → 2108 + 77 = 2185

--------------------------------------------------------------------
4.  Sum of the neighbours
--------------------------------------------------------------------
2025 + 2027 + 1873 + 1874 + 2184 + 2185  
= (2025+2027) + (1873+1874) + (2184+2185)  
= 4052 + 3747 + 4369  
= 12168

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Answer
--------------------------------------------------------------------
12168
----
